<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 30 at 10:08PM EDT  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...Foggy Tonight...
Plan on areas of fog tonight from southeast West Virginia, through
the New River and Roanoke Valleys, into Southside Virginia and
northern North Carolina. Locations where it rained on Saturday
will occasionally see dense fog, with visibilities less than one
half mile.
If you are traveling tonight, be prepared for rapid changes in
visibility. Slow down and allow for extra time to reach your
destination. Use low beam headlights and give yourself plenty of
space to react when following other vehicles.</description>
